          "text": "<br><br><b><i class='far fa-clock'></i> 09:00 - 16:00 - monday</b> <br>Geamăna tour - we will decide together if we will visit it by car or by foot. In our way we can stop to one of the oldest monastery from our region - Lupșa - 1421 AD.",
                      }           }         ]       }     },     {       "images": [
